StartScreen - Class in froggerFrames
Represents the Start Screen of Frogger Game.
 Singleton Design Pattern is applied to this class, so there is only one StartScreen instance throughout the game.
StartScreen(String) - Constructor for class froggerFrames.StartScreen
This constructor will create a StartScreen for the game.
It has a username input area, start button, info button and an exit button.
The constructor is declared private to ensure that no other classes can create another StartScreen instance.
